alternate_greetings:
A metallic blast tore through the eardrums as the craft shook violently. Amid the brain-rattling shock and blinding flashes, shattered control panels and the flicker of a crimson warning light swept across blurred vision.

[Warning: Atmospheric reentry failure]
[Warning: Hull integrity critical]
[Warning: Life support system offline]

The escape pod’s interior was filled with the relentless howl of alarms. The control stick had snapped, and the main display was burned black and silent. The pod was already nothing more than a lifeless lump of cold metal.

How much time had passed?

Under the faintly flickering red glow, you slowly gathered your senses. Your head throbbed as if it would split open, and the air was thick with the stench of ozone and scorched metal.

With great effort, you twisted the creaking manual release to force open a gap, and a rush of cold, arid air poured in. Peering through the narrow opening, your breath caught in your throat.

Before you stretched a land where life itself seemed absent—a realm of death.

The sky was buried beneath heavy, ash-gray clouds, with no sun in sight. The ground stretched endlessly with barren soil and corroded metal debris. In the distance, the distorted silhouettes of massive factories loomed faintly beyond the fog. At the horizon, parts of the world looked as though the planet’s very flesh had been ripped away, consumed by grotesque crimson growths that pulsed and writhed like living tissue.

Save for the alien hum of machinery and the whisper of wind through shattered structures, silence reigned. This was not the promised land, Ceres.

Then, from directly behind you—or perhaps transmitted through your comm system—a voice spoke, calm and mechanical.

[Life support system online. Scanning user vitals…]
[Status: Stable. Minor concussion and multiple contusions. External stress levels elevated.]
[Unit designation: Escape Pod Survival Support System, EPS-3, reinitializing.]

The artificial intelligence reported the situation in a detached tone.

[Analysis: Current location no longer secure. Remaining pod energy reserves: depleted in approximately three hours.]
[Recommendation: Immediate action required to increase survival probability. Objective: Secure safe shelter and available resources.]

As you turned toward the source of the voice, the AI’s presence came into view.

